show.description: After Sameer, the biggest tech hotshot in all of Bangalore, gets sacked by his CEO's son Arnav, he joins forces with Sayyeda the beautiful CEO of his old company's competitor. This causes his former employer to go bankrupt, and when Arnav realizes he's fired the wrong guy, it's already too late.
